

 There are so many cases when we have to fetch some data from the server to our web Application or even send some data from our web application 
 to the Server .

 But , As we know React is a Library used for creating and building user INterfaces .SO , They do not tend to make HTTP requests on their own 

 So , to use the fetched data from the sever in a React Component we use HTTP library -

 There are so many HTTP Library , and Among which we will be using Axios.
